cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper presents a novel framework for automatic learning of complex strategies in human decision making, which involves machine learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions an application in autonomous highway driving, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the scope of industrial applications, which could relate to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
